messages.message:
Hey, does anyone know what the status is with Resistant AI integrations within AI Hub?

cc @Kaustubh (KD) @Nico
We really have not progressed on this. Is there a client requirement on this

In the Adyen POV we are running we are competing as two separate vendors with RAI. compared to other vendors who do both extraction and fraud detection as a single vendor (Inscribe). It would be advantageous to be able to sell as a single offering
We haven't prioritized this from a product perspective, I think at one point Lee had mentioned that there was snippet he was working on. Unsure if this is still accurate or if there was a handoff
